creator: Anonymous
description:
LibriVox recording of A Little Girl to Her Flowers by Anonymous.
Read in English by LisaRubio; Larry Wilson
This is a small volume with short poems about flowers. Listeners may wish to refer to the online text, which includes very neat illustrations. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

M4B Audiobook (3MB)
